{
  "stem": "3973.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only difference was there was a barrack in the camp which was surrounded by its own wire.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the people who were in there, they couldn't go out and mix with the others, and nobody could go in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I asked, who are these people?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Must be very dangerous if they have a camp within the camp of this particular group.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Says, who are they?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They are-- they are Jehovah's Witnesses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're all Germans mostly, and they were locked up because they wouldn't go along with Hitler.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wouldn't serve in the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I says, why did they lock them up?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He says, because otherwise, they will go and preach to others.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They are considered too dangerous for that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But what they told me is, these people were the only ones who were not victims because they were told by signing a statement denouncing their religion was enough to set them free.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they wouldn't go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this is something which was totally unusual, because any one of us would-- can you imagine signing a piece of paper to get out?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I mean, it was, there was a talk of the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were there, most of them, going back to 1933-34.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Anyway, so, these were-- these people were the ones-- who were-- they supported one another.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They always had good positions in the kitchen, or working for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So the Germans trusted them for babysitters, or maybe as barbers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They wouldn't cut their throats , and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So as a result, they had good positions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And these people were known to always support one another, help one another.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They was-- they were human.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The only humans in the camp really stood out and made a powerful impression.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, none.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
